      "name": "Primary hemolysis benchmark validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index compared against PIV and hemolysis measurements from FDA generic centrifugal blood pump experiments. RH < 1 satisfied across all 5 operating points.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/cfd-benchmark-run-2024",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/piv-experimental-2024"
