      "name": "Mesh independence study — discretization error quantification",
      "description": "Grid convergence index (GCI) computed across three systematically refined meshes (2.1M, 8.4M, 33.6M elements). GCI < 2.3% on hemolysis index QoI at all operating points. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence.",
